<p>
<lb n="1"/>Eṇṭicaiyil mālyāṉai yeṭṭu miḷaippāṟiyate, yaṇṭar perumāḷaraṅkaṟku taṇṭamiḻ ter ma
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṭṭār poḻil koyil vāḻ ca<hi rend="grantha">kra</hi>rāyaṉu miṉ ṟeṭṭāṉai kaṭṭiṉāṉeṉṟu <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied> maṭṭār toṭaicca<hi rend="grantha">kra</hi>
<lb n="3"/>rāyaṉ matilaraṅkaṟ, keṭṭāṉai kaṭṭiṉā neṉṟañci neṭṭurakaṉ, paiviṭā veḻupaṭi cūḻticai kāppo
<lb n="4" break="no"/>r, kaiviṭārāṉai kaḻuttu 
